OL,3,CCrash kills 7-year-old boy
OL,5,FDerbyshire Police are appealing for
OL,6,Fwitnesses following a crash in Sutton-
OL,7,Fin-Ashfield which claimed the life of
OL,8,Fa 7-year-old boy.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to
OL,11,Freports of a crash involving a child
OL,12,Fand a car on the A38 Kings Mill Road
OL,13,Fnear Kingfisher Way, at 8.26pm on
OL,14,FTuesday 10 March.
OL,16,FLogan Parker aged 7 was pronounced
OL,17,Fdead at the scene.
OL,19,FPolice say he and his family live in
OL,20,Fthe area and are now being looked
OL,21,Fafter by officers.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/4
