OL,3,CCrash kills 7-year-old boy
OL,5,FDerbyshire Police have said the driver
OL,6,Fstopped at the scene and is helping
OL,7,Fthem with their inquiries.
OL,9,FThe A38 was closed in both directions
OL,10,Fand later reopened.
OL,12,FPaying tribute to Logan, his mum said:
OL,13,F"In memory of a boy who will remain
OL,14,Fseven forever. Always unconditionally
OL,15,Floved and cherished, you will never,
OL,16,Fever be forgotten.
OL,18,F"There are no words other than you are
OL,19,Fthe most beautiful, happy and
OL,20,Fmischievous special boy ` full of
OL,21,Flove, light and adventure.
OL,26,@uD@AOUzD@AOU
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/4
