OL,5,F"We will miss you so much. Rest my
OL,6,Fsuper angel. Your memory will live on
OL,7,Fforever. This is not goodbye but a
OL,8,F'see you soon'.
OL,10,F"Love from mum and family."
OL,12,FDetective Inspector Jamie Moore, said:
OL,13,F"This is a devastating incident and
OL,14,Four thoughts are with Logan's family,
OL,15,Ffriends and loved ones.
OL,17,F"The circumstances are being
OL,18,Finvestigated and we would ask the
OL,19,Fprivacy of the family is respected at
OL,20,Fthis tragic and difficult time.
OL,26,@mD@AOUrD@[O]uD@AOUyD@AOU
